{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/react with daum-map.1/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"키-발급\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%82%A4-%EB%B0%9C%EA%B8%89\" aria-label=\"키 발급 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>키 발급</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://developers.kakao.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">카카오 개발자사이트</a>에가서 가입후 키발급을 받자</p>\n<h2 id=\"적용하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"적용하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>적용하기</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-code-classlanguage-textpublicindexhtmlcode에-다음-지도-api를-스크립트로-추가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-code-classlanguage-textpublicindexhtmlcode%EC%97%90-%EB%8B%A4%EC%9D%8C-%EC%A7%80%EB%8F%84-api%EB%A5%BC-%EC%8A%A4%ED%81%AC%EB%A6%BD%ED%8A%B8%EB%A1%9C-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"1 code classlanguage textpublicindexhtmlcode에 다음 지도 api를 스크립트로 추가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. <code class=\"language-text\">public/index.html</code>에 다음 지도 api를 스크립트로 추가</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text/javascript<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>//dapi.kakao.com/v2/maps/sdk.js?appkey=발급받은키값<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"2-사용하려는-컴포넌트에-추가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EB%A0%A4%EB%8A%94-%EC%BB%B4%ED%8F%AC%EB%84%8C%ED%8A%B8%EC%97%90-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"2 사용하려는 컴포넌트에 추가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 사용하려는 컴포넌트에 추가</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">declare</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> daum<span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token builtin\">any</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Map</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">React</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Component <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">componentDidMount</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> el <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'map'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> daumMap <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">daum</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>maps<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">Map</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>el<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      center<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">daum</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>maps<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">LatLng</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">33.450701</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">126.570667</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Fragment<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Map\"</span> id<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"map\"</span> style<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"width:1000px;height:500px\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Fragment<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> Map<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이 때 TSlint가 daum키워드 때문에 계속 오류를 내뿜는다. 이렇게 써드파티 라이브러리를 타입스크립트에서 사용할 땐 <a href=\"http://www.albertgao.xyz/2016/08/10/how-to-use-a-third-party-library-in-typescript-with-or-without-its-type-definition-file/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">여러방법</a>으로 피할 수 있지만 간단히 <code class=\"language-text\">declare var someValue:any</code>를 사용 할 수도 있다.</p>\n<p>리액트에는 여러 라이프사이클이 존재한다. 그 중 <code class=\"language-text\">componentDidMount()</code>은 컴포넌트가 화면에 나타나게 됐을 때 호출된다. 주로 DOM을 사용하는 외부 라이브러리 연동을 하거나 데이터를 요청하기위해 ajax요청을 하거나, DOM 속성을 읽거나 직접 변경하는 작업을 진행할 수 있다.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">... declared but its value is never read</code> 이 오류 메세지가 뜬다면 <code class=\"language-text\">tsconfig.json</code>파일에서 <code class=\"language-text\">noUnusedLocals</code>를 <code class=\"language-text\">false</code>로 바꾸면된다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"참고한-링크\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0%ED%95%9C-%EB%A7%81%ED%81%AC\" aria-label=\"참고한 링크 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참고한 링크</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://velopert.com/3631\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">누구든지 하는 리액트 5편: LifeCycle API</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.albertgao.xyz/2016/08/10/how-to-use-a-third-party-library-in-typescript-with-or-without-its-type-definition-file/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">How to use a third party library in Typescript with or without its type definition file?</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Microsoft/TypeScript/issues/19700\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://github.com/Microsoft/TypeScript/issues/19700</a></li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"키 발급 카카오 개발자사이트에가서 가입후 키발급을 받자 적용하기 1. 에 다음 지도 api를 스크립트로 추가 2. 사용하려는 컴포넌트에 추가 이 때 TSlint가 daum키워드 때문에 계속 오류를 내뿜는다. 이렇게 써드파티 라이브러리를 타입스크립트에…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/react%20with%20daum-map.1/#%ED%82%A4-%EB%B0%9C%EA%B8%89\">키 발급</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/react%20with%20daum-map.1/#%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">적용하기</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/react%20with%20daum-map.1/#1-code-classlanguage-textpublicindexhtmlcode%EC%97%90-%EB%8B%A4%EC%9D%8C-%EC%A7%80%EB%8F%84-api%EB%A5%BC-%EC%8A%A4%ED%81%AC%EB%A6%BD%ED%8A%B8%EB%A1%9C-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\">1. <code class=\"language-text\">public/index.html</code>에 다음 지도 api를 스크립트로 추가</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/react%20with%20daum-map.1/#2-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EB%A0%A4%EB%8A%94-%EC%BB%B4%ED%8F%AC%EB%84%8C%ED%8A%B8%EC%97%90-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\">2. 사용하려는 컴포넌트에 추가</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/react%20with%20daum-map.1/#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0%ED%95%9C-%EB%A7%81%ED%81%AC\">참고한 링크</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/react with daum-map.1/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"creat-react-app-typescript 에 다음지도 적용하기","date":"Jul 15, 2018","tags":["react","다음 지도 api"],"keywords":["R0k's log","padawanR0k"],"update":"Jan 01, 0001"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/react with daum-map.1/","series":[],"lastmod":"2018-07-15"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2027115977","694178885"]}